title: EYL #194 Don Peebles on Billion Dollar Real Estate Lessons & NYC's First Black Owned Skyscraper
itunes:title: EYL #194 Don Peebles on Billion Dollar Real Estate Lessons & NYC's First Black Owned Skyscraper
description:
Don Peebles on Billion Dollar Real Estate Lessons & NYC's First Black Owned Skyscraper 

 

We sat down with Donahue Peebles who is the largest black real estate developer in American history. He's also estimated to be a billionaire, and a business genius. 

He spoke about his plans to build Affirmation Tower, which will be the only black owned and black developed skyscraper in New York City. He also spoke about the current state of real estate, private equity, venture capital, and real estate development. #donpeebles #realestate #earnyourleisure 

EYL University: https://www.eyluniversity.com

Link for Invest Fest: https://investfest.com/
